{"tid":801308,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天價剪髮修眉】戇男幫襯理髮店 埋單$4.6萬被嚇呆","createTime":"2018-08-31T13:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T04:48:31.000Z","uid":28765,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b04639b227c5ed2e4b9e7dfeca157823b881a62","tid":801308,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:53:10.000Z","msg":"（新增動新聞、更新照片）剪髮修眉，要近4萬元人民幣（下同，約4.6萬港元），同搶根本沒有分別！浙江杭州就有一名男子，到當地一間理髮店修髮際線和修眉，沒想到要結帳時要3.9萬元（約4.47萬港元），報警後經協調，最後也要支付2,500元（約2,866港元）。<br />\n事發於本月28日，涉事的18歲男子小吳，到一間SPA店理髮，對方說有免費項目可以體驗，他坐下後，有人將一個單據遞給他，要他簽名。小吳表示，當時店內有兩、三個人將他圍起來，他還沒看細看，就被迫簽下單據。結果理髮及修眉後，店家卻要求小吳支付3.9萬元，隨後打折也要1.8萬元（約2.06萬港元）。小吳無奈下唯有報警，但也要給2,500元。<br />\n小吳謂，他原本並沒有要求修眉，卻被店方強行加進去，但效果不太理想，原本他的眉毛顯示他凶惡，但修完後，同學說，他比以前更為凶惡。店方則指，收費合理，小吳雙鬢及眉毛經過處理後不會再生雜毛。<br />\n事件曝光後有戲劇性發展，小吳日前在微博發文指，這次的理髮事件已經圓滿落幕，店家不僅道歉也退還所有的費用，相信是因為受到當局及網民的壓力，他要感謝一眾網友的支持。<br />\n搜狐網/ 微博  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535714852_2065.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535714852_2065.jpg&h=c314bfd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小吳用$4.6萬天價修的眉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535642292_2c5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535642292_2c5e.jpg&h=c46b7126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小吳在理髮店剪髮修眉，被索$4.6萬天價。事件曝光後，他在微博上表示，店方已退款了事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180831/58626946\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58626946&d=wlg5qpysbMwI8blMwSHqzfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=e170de00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58626946&h=82748d68\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180831/58626946</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/6/69/Hamgachang.gif/revision/latest?cb=20061105121804\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F6%2F69%2FHamgachang.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20061105121804&h=c7ab5daa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"912ed2a372ed6e878956a5b47322654d6031a3b3","tid":801308,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c43508b0f906670bc7ad4c83a1b9926645ecd79","tid":801308,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:56:11.000Z","msg":"原本他的眉毛顯示他凶惡，但修完後，同學說，他比以前更為凶惡。"},{"pid":"6847d91bc84a10eba2b4bbf38f24ad6fcd72f822","tid":801308,"uid":118758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T04:48:31.000Z","msg":"條友而家係大陸好似好撚紅"}]}